<br>
Solo - <B>Martial Artist</B> Play one and you'll see why.<br>
          <B>Doctor</B> Believe it or not - They can solo :P No clue for how long though.<br>
          <B>Soldier</B> one hit wonders. :) Very good.<br>
          <B>Adventurer</B> Heals, AC buffs, Damage shields.. they are pretty good :P<br>
<br>
PVP - Depends on how you play. Every class is superior to another.. but vulnerable to the other. My nanotech can take ANY  melee class without getting touched. (I have a good Vektor ND :P)... but gets waxed if a ranged class attacks him(IE Agent, Soldier, anything of the sort who uses a good weapon)...My Enforcer and MA can take anyone if they can get close.. Enforcer usually kills them in one hit. :) Cept other enforcers.. they usually take a few hits. <3 Sledgehammer.  And my MA can usually take anyone out with how fast he hits, his crit rate(thx to crit buffs), and his Bird of Prey. But if either of'em get rooted..they're effed. :) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umaijun.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Maijun</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/17/01 10:40:42 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Opinions on the best group/solo/pvp professions?</span><hr size=1> Best Solo- Most likely an Enforcer.<br>
